<span style="font-size:12pt"><span arial="" narrow="" style="font-family:"><span style="color:#3d3935"><span style="font-weight:normal">In response to changing marketplace conditions, Shashi Hotel is committed to ensuring our customers experience flexibility during these challenging times.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif"><span style="color:#3d3935"><span style="font-weight:normal">​</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>

<ul>
